    "This function provides a roadmap for restoring operations with the help of various cybersecurity solutions.• Recovery planning-Recovery planning involves maintaining, testing, and implementing processes and procedures to restore systems or assets that have been impacted by cybersecurity incidents.",
    "It includes the timely recovery of lost data and functionality to ensure that everything is functioning as intended.",
    "AI-based recovery planning automates data and system recovery, including malware removal, in response to cybersecurity incidents.",
    "It enhances speed and accuracy, minimizing downtime and mitigating impacts.",
    "However, no significant research in this area was identified in the literature review.• Improvements-This category focuses on reviewing the security incident to identify areas for improvement in recovery planning processes."
